SUMMARY:Electoral Working Group Campaign Operations Meeting
DTSTAMP:20260327T062527Z
DTSTART:20260408T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join our Electoral Working Group’s Campaign Operations meeting 
	series: come learn\\\, plan\\\, and execute the operational aspects of our
	 endorsed campaigns – with tasks and trainings on field\\\, fundraising\\\
	, communications\\\, and internal member mobilization. Every Wednesday at 
